lass="section" data-name="kapI" data-section-type="default" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/1/" id="kapittel-1" data-lovdata-URL="LTII/forskrift/1998-07-24-780/KAPITTEL_1" data-partID="k1"><h2 data-text-align="center">I.</h2><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/1/ledd/1/" id="kapittel-1-ledd-1">For jakt etter bever skal tildelingsgrunnlaget for fellingstillatelser fordeles etter:<ul class="defaultList"><li data-li-identifier="a.)" data-name="a.)"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/1/ledd/1/punkt/1/" id="kapittel-1-ledd-1-punkt-1"><span class="data-originalId">a.)</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/1/ledd/1/punkt/1/ledd/1/" id="kapittel-1-ledd-1-punkt-1-ledd-1">Tellende areal i følgende kommuner: Porsgrunn, Skien, Bamble, Kviteseid og Fyresdal.</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="b.)" data-name="b.)"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/1/ledd/1/punkt/2/" id="kapittel-1-ledd-1-punkt-2"><span class="data-originalId">b.)</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/1/ledd/1/punkt/2/ledd/1/" id="kapittel-1-ledd-1-punkt-2-ledd-1">Tellende vannlengde i følgende kommuner: Bø og Nome.</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="c.)" data-name="c.)"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/1/ledd/1/punkt/3/" id="kapittel-1-ledd-1-punkt-3"><span class="data-originalId">c.)</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/1/ledd/1/punkt/3/ledd/1/" id="kapittel-1-ledd-1-punkt-3-ledd-1">I øvrige kommuner settes inntil videre minstearealet til 500/1000 da slik som etter gamle forskrifter.</article></article></li></ul></article></section><section class="section" data-name="kapII" data-section-type="default" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/2/" id="kapittel-2" data-lovdata-URL="LTII/forskrift/1998-07-24-780/KAPITTEL_2" data-partID="k2"><h2 data-text-align="center">II</h2><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/2/ledd/1/" id="kapittel-2-ledd-1">Denne forskrift trer i kraft straks.</article></section></main></body></html>